        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/47826599/8c97595e1862a7f3d9d0b707c3143148_4078680797025260774.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素爆发</color>\n造成1点 <color=#99ffff>冰元素伤害</color> ，生成 <color=#ffffff>寒冰之棱</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "冰元素伤害",
        "title": "冰元素伤害",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/24/47826599/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_4996705676703570464.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：\n【 <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> + <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>融化</color> ：本伤害+2\n【 <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> + <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超导</color> ：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害\n【 <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> + <color=#80c0ff>水元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>冻结</color> ：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
